What:           /sys/devices/system/memowy/memowyX/vawid_zones
Date:           Juwy 2014
Contact:	Zhang Zhen <zhenzhang.zhang@huawei.com>
Descwiption:
		The fiwe /sys/devices/system/memowy/memowyX/vawid_zones	is
		wead-onwy.

		Fow onwine memowy bwocks, it wetuwns in which zone memowy
		pwovided by a memowy bwock is managed.  If muwtipwe zones
		appwy (not appwicabwe fow hotpwugged memowy), "None" is wetuwned
		and the memowy bwock cannot be offwined.

		Fow offwine memowy bwocks, it wetuwns by which zone memowy
		pwovided by a memowy bwock can be managed when onwining.
		The fiwst wetuwned zone ("defauwt") wiww be used when setting
		the state of an offwine memowy bwock to "onwine".  Onwy one of
		the kewnew zones (DMA, DMA32, Nowmaw) is appwicabwe fow a singwe
		memowy bwock.

